== IMIRIMO YAKOZE ==


'''Urujeni Martine''' ni [[umugore]] w'umunyarwandakazi w’[[imyaka]] 50. '''Urujeni Mertine'''  yatorerwa kuba Umuyobozi wungirije w’[[Umujyi wa Kigali]],<ref>https://umuryango.rw/amakuru/mu-rwanda/politiki/article/kigali-urujeni-martine-yatorewe-kuba-umuyobozi-wungirije-ushinzwe-ubukungu-n</ref> ushinzwe Ubukungu n’imibereho myiza y’[[Abaturage Rusange|abaturage]], akaba yaratorewe mu matora yabaye kuru uyu wa Gatanu tariki 25 Werurwe 2022,<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/new-city-vice-mayor-prioritise-welfare-improvement</ref> Urujeni akaba yagize amajwi 298 kuri 397 y’Inteko itora.<ref>https://www.ktpress.rw/2022/03/urujeni-martine-elected-vice-mayor-city-of-kigali/</ref> ntabwo ari mushya mu ubuyobozi   kuko amaze igihe ayobora Ishami rishinzwe kwegereza ubutabera abaturage, muri Minisiteri y’Ubutabera.<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/amakuru/article/urujeni-martine-abaye-umuyobozi-w-umujyi-wa-kigali-wungirije-ushinzwe-ubukungu-n-imibereho-myiza</ref>Yabaye kandi Umuhuzabikorwa wa gahunda yo kwegereza ubutabera [[Abaturage Rusange|abaturage]] (Coordinator of Maison d’Access à la Justice, MAJ),<ref>https://umuseke.rw/2021/06/amavugurura-yikoranabuhanga-rikoreshwa-muri-cyamunara-azarandura-uburiganya-bwabagamo/amp/</ref> anaba umuyobozi wungirije muri MAJ ushinzwe uburenganzira bw’[[abana]]<ref>https://flash.rw/2019/04/04/icyo-tuzasaba-rib-ni-ugukurikiza-amategeko-ntibahutireho-ngo-bamushyire-muri-kasho-urujeni-martine/</ref> no kurwanya ihohoterwa rishingiye ku gitsina.<ref>https://igihe.com/amakuru/u-rwanda/article/umujyi-wa-kigali-wabonye-umuyobozi-wungirije-mushya</ref><ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/new-city-vice-mayor-prioritise-welfare-improvement</ref>

